I"=<p>First turn of the header with <code class="highlighter-rouge">header: no</code>. Then add an image to with the following code. The caption is optional.
<!--more--></p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>header: no
image:
    title: unsplash_eagle.jpg
    caption: This is a caption for the header image with link
    caption_url: https://unsplash.com/
</code></pre></div></div>

